          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-1" n="1">The greatest monarch may be stabbed by night,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-2" n="2">And fortune help the murderer in his flight;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-3" n="3">The vilest ruffian may commit a rape,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-4" n="4">Yet safe from injured innocence escape:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-5" n="5">And calumny, by working underground,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-6" n="6">Can, unrevenged, the greatest merit wound.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-7" n="7"><lb/>What's to be done? shall wit and learning choose,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-8" n="8">To live obscure, and have no fame to lose?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-9" n="9">By censure frighted out of honour's road,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-10" n="10">Nor dare to use the gifts by heaven bestowed;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-11" n="11">Or fearless enter in through virtue's gate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-ROGP-line-12" n="12">And buy distinction at the dearest rate?</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
